      "content": "it's not just about taking a break though. i feel like no matter how much i rest, the feeling is still there. it's like there's this fundamental error in me that makes it impossible to actually connect with people. even if i \"embrace who i am,\" i'm still just going to be the weirdo in the corner. what's the point of even trying to make it work if it's just going to be this constant, draining struggle?",
